      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PADOVA (1) was a last-start winner from the inside at this track and distance (19.88) after missing the jump, scoring by a nose. Drawn the rails again and rates the measuring stick. RECONSTRUCTION (8) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 19.87 beating Our Boy Chopper. Should feature again. TARAWI BUSTER (5) is a smart beginner who has shown good improvement at his last two starts, most recently finishing 2nd at Q Straight over 350m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Can measure up. BLACK HORSE (4) did a good job to finish third last time out over 366m at this track (19.90) in a Grade 1/2, the second top-three finish on the trot.",
